graphify-out/

# Visual + reference assets live in Obsidian vault, not the repo
docs/screenshots/
docs/design-handoff/

# Dev-only scaffolding (preview routes, capture scripts, decision records live in vault)
app/internal/preview/
scripts/capture-*.mjs
docs/decisions/
